{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/impove-pixie-expert-profile-page-seo-1","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"f927ae61-011a-5596-866e-adbb151632ab","html":"<h1 id=\"disclaimer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#disclaimer\" aria-label=\"disclaimer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Disclaimer</h1>\n<p>I am no near expert in SEO optimization, but I am a developer who always want to try out and learn new things also help improve company product recognition (gotpixie.com). Also at my level, I think the best way is to improve product overtime rather than try to do the best practice (if I knew one lol).</p>\n<h1 id=\"current-state-of-expert-profile-page-seo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#current-state-of-expert-profile-page-seo\" aria-label=\"current state of expert profile page seo permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Current state of expert profile page SEO</h1>\n<h2 id=\"what-we-achieved\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#what-we-achieved\" aria-label=\"what we achieved permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>What we achieved</h2>\n<p>We using NextJS server side rendering to fetch expert profile in frontend server then give back the user ‚Äúfull HTML‚Äù of the page, it contains basic meta tags link title = ‚ÄúExpert name | Pixie‚Äù, description = Expert bio, image thumbnail attached to profile avatar.</p>\n<p>Also we using <a href=\"https://github.com/garmeeh/next-seo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">next-seo</a> making config SEO a lot easier.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">NextSeo</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>profile<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>lastName<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>profile<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>firstName<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> | Pixie</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">description</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>profile<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>expert<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>headline<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">. </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>profile<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>expert<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>bio<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">openGraph</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    title<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>profile<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>lastName<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>profile<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>firstName<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> | Pixie</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    description<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>profile<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>expert<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>headline<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">. </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>profile<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>expert<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>bio<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    images<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        url<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> profile<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>avatar <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"default-avatar.jpeg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        alt<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"avatar\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>After having all the basic meta tags, we using <a href=\"https://github.com/iamvishnusankar/next-sitemap\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">next-sitemap</a> to generate <code class=\"language-text\">sitemap.xml</code> file that contains all the statics page, <code class=\"language-text\">server-sitemap.xml</code> will first fetch all the experts and map to expert profile url to the sitemap. Then we bring our website to the google console and add that 2 sitemaps, after like a week or 2, we can search expert profile right on Google:</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/pixie-seo-1/Screen%20Shot%202022-03-11%20at%2003.19.45.png\"></p>\n<p>The results:</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/pixie-seo-1/Screen%20Shot%202022-03-11%20at%2003.12.16.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/pixie-seo-1/Screen%20Shot%202022-03-11%20at%2003.22.11.png\"></p>\n<p>Yah, we have our thumbnail when share to social media and Google Search recognized us üéâ</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-problems\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-problems\" aria-label=\"the problems permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The problems</h2>\n<h3 id=\"getting-all-experts-when-generate-server-sitemapxml\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#getting-all-experts-when-generate-server-sitemapxml\" aria-label=\"getting all experts when generate server sitemapxml permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Getting ‚Äúall experts‚Äù when generate <code class=\"language-text\">server-sitemap.xml</code></h3>\n<p>We now have more than 100 expert‚Äôs profiles and when build the app we basically get all 100 profiles in <em>one</em> API call, lol, and yes it did crash when building the docker image.</p>\n<p>To fix this is quite simple, get the backend team to support pagination the get all expert api, and option to get only the expert id, we only need the id to parse url <code class=\"language-text\">gotpixie.com/experts/[id]</code>.</p>\n<p>Also, we need to splitting the sitemap into multiple files when it get too big. In <code class=\"language-text\">next-sitemap.js</code> in root folder adding <code class=\"language-text\">sitemapSize: 3000</code>. When the number of URLs in a sitemap is more than 3000, <code class=\"language-text\">next-sitemap</code> will create sitemap (e.g. sitemap-0.xml, sitemap-1.xml) and index (e.g. sitemap.xml) files.</p>\n<h3 id=\"do-we-need-more-meta-tags\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#do-we-need-more-meta-tags\" aria-label=\"do we need more meta tags permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Do we need more meta tags?</h3>\n<p>Well I think we do, so I go to different famous websites to have a sneak of what they did. I came to conclusion that we will add these type of meta tags:</p>\n<h4 id=\"keywords-meta-tag\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#keywords-meta-tag\" aria-label=\"keywords meta tag permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>keywords meta tag</h4>\n<h4 id=\"twitter-meta-tags\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#twitter-meta-tags\" aria-label=\"twitter meta tags permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Twitter meta tags</h4>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/impove-pixie-expert-profile-page-seo-1","tagSlugs":["/tag/pixie/","/tag/next-js/","/tag/seo/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-10-03T10:59:05.941Z","description":"Improve Pixie product overtime (SEO part 1)","tags":["Pixie","NextJS","SEO"],"title":"Pixie expert profile SEO optimization part 1","socialImage":"/media/nextjs-logo.png"}}},"pageContext":{"